title: International Market Challenge + Raymundo’s Bachelor Party Takes A Hit + Lunchbox Calls Dairy Queen

description:
We all brought in food items from an international market for someone else on the show to eat. Raymundo shares a sad update to his Vegas bachelor party. Plus, Lunchbox calls Dairy Queen to tell them he got a brain freeze from their blizzards and requires medical help!
